luluResponse.responseText: The Commission Classic-Fit Pant 32L always has you covered with elevated comfort.

reviewsEntries.title: Nice and easy
reviewsEntries.reviewText: Bought for my husband as part of a holiday sweat collective promotion. He loves them and wears them often. We appreciate the discount provided.

reviewsEntries.title: You will love these pants!
reviewsEntries.reviewText: My husband loves these pants. He works in a business casual office and they are perfect with a dress shirt or polo. He plans to buy in another colour this week. We find they fit true to size.

reviewsEntries.title: Five stars
reviewsEntries.reviewText: Love the pants, great quality and fit

reviewsEntries.title: Favorite pants
reviewsEntries.reviewText: They’re comfortable, versatile, and look great. I keep coming back to these after trying other styles/brands. Only downside is they only last a year or two before getting holes in the crotch from regular use. I usually just buy another pair when that happens, because they’re the best.

luluResponse.responseText: Thanks for taking the time to share your feedback with us. We'd love to hear more about your experience with your Commission Classic-Fit Pant 32L, and we've sent you a follow-up email to carry on this conversation in more detail.

We're so happy to see how much you love the Commission Classic-Fit Pant 32L. Our Design team likes to surprise us with new colours—we'll put in a good word for you though. Make sure to sign up for product emails to be the first to know when new colours drop.

reviewsEntries.title: Great for business casual dress!

reviewsEntries.title: Finally a model size thay fit perfect
reviewsEntries.reviewText: Excellent fit. Perfect description from manequin or hanger to body. Shopping online no fear because i know the fit will be exact.

reviewsEntries.title: Great Pants
reviewsEntries.reviewText: My husband loves these pants.  He has gotten a bunch over the last couple of years.  He wears them to work everyday.  You can dress them up or down.

luluResponse.responseText: The perfect pants to wear on repeat.

reviewsEntries.title: Perfect pants for pilots!
reviewsEntries.reviewText:
I work as an airline pilot and these are by far the most comfortable pair of business trousers that I’ve ever worn; they have flex where it’s needed, but are fitted and not billowy like a lot of the regular uniform providers. Perfect for long periods of being strapped into a cramped cockpit seat! I’m 6’ tall, 156 lb, with a runner’s physique and the 30”W x 32”L fits me perfectly. 

A couple of things to consider before you purchase if you’re a pilot: the material is not the same as what most blazers are made out of and so might look slightly off. Also, the cuffs are quite narrow and would not work with the ropers/boots that some pilots wear, but they do work with elastic sided boots.

reviewsEntries.title: Perfect length and ease of movement
reviewsEntries.reviewText: Perfect length and ease of movement. I’ve been looking around for the perfect pants for work and this fits my standard, material is nice and good thickness yet I can move freely without any traditional pants restrictions.
